channel.title: My website so far. Please rate and give feedback
channel.description:
Well this is not to advertise but to have some peer review over my website I am working on. This is a new website, and is currently hosted free. I will not pay for a domain until I get the website in tip top shape. Please rate on a scale of 1-10 and report all bugs and grammatical errors you find. (please don't post if the error is already listed) Oh, and also rate the layout, and looks of the website.
Website URL: [url=http://spikeyjournal.co.nr/]http://spikeyjournal.co.nr/[/url] Known Bugs:
1.The Nav Bar does not load on any pages except for the home page 2. 3. 4. 5. Please report if any more are found
Grammatical Errors:
None so far! WOOT!
1. Spelling mistake: Jounral Entries Coming Soon! 2. 3. 4. 5.
